        "narrative": false,
        "demo_actions": false,
        "screenshot": false,
        "visual": false,
        "design_plan": false
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- From there, the agent becomes easier for the business to use.\n- People do not need to open a builder tool.\n- Invoice assurance can show up where they already work, including Teams through M365.",
      "demo_actions": "Move to the M365 or Teams surface. Show the autopilot or agent entry point in Teams.",
